for install apache

sudo yum install httpd



for redirect 

Redirect "/page1.html" "/page2.html"




for restart httpd

systemctl restart httpd

Ask for username and password when accessing a directory.

AuthType Basic
AuthName “Restricted web page”
AuthUserFile “/var/www/html/.htpasswd”
require valid-user


 Create a directory then allow access to one of your classmates only.

Require host localhost
Require ip 127.0.0.1
Require 192.168
Require 10


Change the default index page to be default.html instead of index.html

DirectoryIndex index.html
DirectoryIndex index.html defult.html




